to run this program
please do autoreconf -i on Centos A
please make clean before compiling on any system
afterwards, please run ./runscript.sh instead of doing configure && make
./runscript will configure, and make install
afterwards cd ../..
and cd into build/bin-- the binaries will have been installed into the build directory.
three levels of debugging work; they're not pretty, but they work.

-l will write to a logging file

-h will print the usage statement for key

